snippet: Jordan Leopold scored the tiebreaking goal at 5:33 of the third period, leading the St. Louis Blues to a 4-1 victory over the Minnesota Wild on Thursday night....

headline.print_headline: Leopold Scores in 3rd as Blues Beat Wild, 4-1
headline.main: Leopold Scores in 3rd as Blues Beat Wild, 4-1

lead_paragraph: Jordan Leopold scored the tiebreaking goal at 5:33 of the third period, leading the St. Louis Blues to a 4-1 victory over the Minnesota Wild on Thursday night.
